      <div class="flex flex-row gap-4">
        <a class="w-fit p-4 text-neutral-100 font-bold bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg drop-shadow-xl hover:bg-transparent border-solid border-2 border-neutral-900 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-all" href="/products">View Products</a>
        <a class="w-fit p-4 text-neutral-500 font-bold border-solid border-2 border-neutral-500 rounded-lg hover:border-neutral-900 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-all drop-shadow-xl" href="/products/create">Add a Product</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-neutral-400">Made by Chernysh Artem, here is my <a href="https://github.com/TemaTech" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-neutral-900 transition-all">Github</a> account</p>
